   <head>Epigrammi - XIX. De Ferdinando juniore.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Corniger aesculea Faunus recubabat in umbra;</l>
     <l n="2">Quum prope latrantes sensit adesse canes.</l>
     <l n="3">Mox Juvenem Superis similem divinaque tela</l>
     <l n="4">Conspiciens, trepido sic movet ora sono:</l>
     <l n="5">Seu Mars, sive alto Phoebus descendis Olympo;</l>
     <l n="6">Jam jam linquo omnes te veniente feras.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
